<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n08125f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08125f">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08125f"> 125(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> tot<font color="green">[ies]</font> quot<font color="green">[ies]</font> / Portiuncula</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">On <font color="green">[the Feast of the Rosary]</font> a plenary indulgence <i>toties quoties</i> is granted upon certain conditions to all who visit &hellip; the Rosary chapel or statue of Our Lady. This has been called the &ldquo;Portiuncula&rdquo; of the Rosary. <small> <a name="CECRA" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CECRA"><cite title="source">&ldquo;Coemgen&rdquo;, &ldquo;Rosary&rdquo; and &ldquo;Albigenses&rdquo;</cite></a> <cite a>Catholic Encyclopaedia</cite></a> (1911) XIII, &lsquo;Rosary&rsquo; 189a</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
